Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.44,0:22:30.95,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}令人不禁想要放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.28,0:22:37.00,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}坦露自己的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.33,0:22:41.88,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}任凭此身沉浮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.50,0:22:45.34,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}你握紧冰冷的十指
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.34,0:22:48.22,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}脸上是悲切的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.22,0:22:51.18,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我无言以对
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.39,0:22:54.14,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}只有视野渐渐模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.31,0:22:57.10,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}不需言语粉饰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.10,0:23:00.02,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}有始必定有终
